My sister Gigi and I are waiting patiently for Santa 🎅🏼 to arrive.

Of course, I am on the #NiceList but Gigi is on the #NaughtyList 

I have already sent Santa my extensive Christmas list 📜🎁🎁🎁🎁🎁

Merry Christmas 🎄and Happy Holidays ❤️.

I love and appreciate all of my friends and family!

I hope Santa 🎅🏼 brought you everything you wanted.

#GodBless #jesusisthereasonfortheseason

🎉💗 The US federal government recognizes 10 National holidays, but today they have added 1 more.

Today is the eleventh holiday, and it is “ Coco’s 9th birthday” 🎉🎂🥳

Yep, today is my birthday and I plan on 2023 being my best year yet!!! 😉

#SuperBowl 

Who are you cheering for:

Eagles 🏈 Chiefs 

Or Rihanna 🎶 😎

“Never iron a four-leaf clover, because you don’t want to press your luck.”

Irish Proverb- 🍀

From my Brother Zeus who passed away, but I miss him very much!

#WorldBeeDay 🐝 

Thank you PETA for sharing this amazing information on bees. 

Celebrate #WorldBeeDay by acknowledging their emotions - yes, they have them too! 🐝

Research shows bees can even feel PTSD-like symptoms, recognize different human faces, process long-term memories while sleeping, & even possibly dream. 

-PETA 

🐝

Definitely my mom’s favorite day of the year #NationalWineDay 🍷

When you get a hangover from wine, it’s called The Grape Depression. 🍇🤣

Who else is excited about #BarbieTheMovie 🩷🩷🩷

“The best way to make a friend is to be a friend“

-Barbie 👱🏻‍♀️

🐶💖🎉🎂 Happy Birthday, to my sweet sister, Gigi 💖🎉 Today she is 9️⃣ years old! 

Although I love Gigi, she still tries to boss me around and I am 9 1/2 so clearly I am the boss of her 😉😘

Check out my super awesome elevated feeder from my amazing friends @nibbleypets . 🩷🌸

I have to use an elevated feeder to eat and drink because of my spine disorder and for the first time I can do it in style. 😎🍽️

This feeder is high end quality and beautifully constructed.

Thank you. 😘❤️

As we roll into fall, and Halloween 🎃 is approaching, I decided to bust out my fall wardrobe🍁.

We had a terribly hot summer here in Texas, but the last couple of days have been absolutely beautiful! 🌤️

Let’s Go @rangers ⚾️

💙❤️💙❤️

Game 3 / we are up 2-0

Happy Halloween! 🎃☠️

Here are a few of my favorite Halloween costumes over the years. 

Which one is your favorite? 👻

Officially 18 days until Santa 🎅🏼 comes to visit me.

Seriously he cannot come soon enough, trying to stay on the “nice list” is exhausting! 🎄

🎉 I am 1️⃣0️⃣ years old today, sheesh where does the time go 🤔

“Life is 10% what happens to you and 90% how you react to it” -Chuck Swindoll
